And look at this.

19:28.775 --> 19:31.880
Surely goodness and mercy shall follow me.

19:32.982 --> 19:33.904
He's in front of me.

19:33.964 --> 19:37.730
He's beside me and he's behind me.

19:38.672 --> 19:43.199
Now that is, that's a formula for success.

19:45.563 --> 19:47.186
God, God is with you.

19:49.538 --> 19:51.541
He's in front of me, giving me direction.

19:52.122 --> 19:53.865
He's beside me, comforting me.

19:54.846 --> 19:58.071
And he's behind me for when I get it wrong.

19:58.992 --> 19:59.393
You know what?

19:59.493 --> 20:00.955
From time to time, we get it wrong.

20:00.995 --> 20:01.556
We mess up.

20:02.838 --> 20:07.285
But his grace and his mercy in 2026 is more than enough.

20:08.427 --> 20:10.770
You've heard me say this so many times, and I'll keep saying it.

20:11.912 --> 20:13.334
You can't fall from grace.

20:13.695 --> 20:14.976
You could only fall into grace.

20:16.959 --> 20:18.642
Grace is there to catch us.

20:21.474 --> 20:27.303
If you only know the God of grace and you don't know the God of guidance, your life isn't going to go anywhere.

20:30.948 --> 20:36.477
So yes, he's there for when we fall, but he's also there to move our lives forward.

20:36.497 --> 20:37.198
He's our shepherd.

20:38.720 --> 20:40.102
So I feel like we're good to go.

20:40.383 --> 20:41.965
We can't lose in 2026.

20:42.025 --> 20:43.988
Will there be valley experiences?

20:44.028 --> 20:46.672
There could well be, but he's in front of me.

20:47.494 --> 20:50.418
He's beside me and he's right behind me.

20:51.522 --> 20:52.924
We have nothing to fear.

20:54.846 --> 20:58.791
So these are some declarations that are put together for this brand new year.

20:58.831 --> 20:59.812
I'm going to pray for you.

21:01.294 --> 21:04.498
And then we can let you get back to your holidays.

21:06.200 --> 21:10.145
Here's a declaration for 2026 from Psalm 23.

21:10.225 --> 21:13.228
The Lord is my shepherd.

21:13.549 --> 21:14.310
Here's the promise.

21:14.770 --> 21:16.052
I will be blessed.

21:16.472 --> 21:21.138
I speak blessing over you, your family and your loved ones.

21:21.602 --> 21:22.423
in this coming year.

21:23.244 --> 21:26.168
He makes me lie down in green pastures.

21:26.268 --> 21:30.374
The promise I will be planted in pleasant places.

21:31.896 --> 21:36.742
Declaration three, he leads me beside the still waters.

21:37.644 --> 21:42.009
I will be refreshed from deep and fulfilling waters.

21:43.051 --> 21:43.391
Amen.

21:44.653 --> 21:48.819
Declaration four, he restores my soul.

21:50.180 --> 21:51.442
I will continually

21:51.906 --> 21:54.389
be restored to wholeness.

21:56.171 --> 22:01.196
Declaration five, he leads me in the paths of righteousness for his name's sake.

22:02.237 --> 22:07.804
I will always be confident my steps are ordered by the law.

22:07.844 --> 22:11.748
He's going to order every step as you take them this coming year.

22:13.330 --> 22:16.033
He is my rod and staff which comfort me.

22:17.174 --> 22:20.978
I will fear no evil thing for God is with me.

22:21.762 --> 22:22.343
He's with me.

22:24.066 --> 22:29.474
He prepares a table of blessing for me in the presence of my enemies.

22:31.136 --> 22:34.762
I will never let opposition rob me of my inheritance.

22:35.403 --> 22:37.366
You have an inheritance in Christ today.

22:38.668 --> 22:42.414
He anoints my head with oil, my cup overflows.

22:43.716 --> 22:50.546
I will always wear the crown of the anointing and think on things above and beyond my present love.

22:51.682 --> 22:53.565
Amen.

22:53.585 --> 22:57.690
He has shown his goodness and mercy to me continually.

22:59.432 --> 23:05.461
Here's the declaration, I will always leave evidence of God's goodness and mercy wherever I go.

23:07.283 --> 23:07.924
Just two more.

23:08.965 --> 23:12.871
He has shown his goodness and mercy to me continually.

23:15.594 --> 23:16.135
Number 10.

23:17.437 --> 23:21.362
He has provided a place for me in his house.

23:21.634 --> 23:22.055
forever.

23:23.116 --> 23:28.563
I will always live to build His house in the light of eternity.

23:29.605 --> 23:32.008
In Jesus' name, amen.

23:32.809 --> 23:36.474
I want us to carry those declarations into this new year.

23:37.015 --> 23:43.424
Psalm 23, He's in front of me, He's beside me, and He's behind me.

23:44.145 --> 23:49.392
If you believe it, I want you to shout a big amen at your television or at your laptop right now.

23:49.792 --> 23:50.994
In Jesus' name,

23:51.234 --> 23:52.456
Amen.

23:52.476 --> 23:53.197
Praise God.

23:53.898 --> 23:54.839
We thank you God.

23:56.041 --> 23:58.224
I want to pray for one more group of people.

23:59.206 --> 24:05.375
Maybe you've just stumbled across soul church on YouTube or Facebook and you started to watch.

24:07.038 --> 24:09.321
Some of the things I said, they've resonated with you.

24:10.082 --> 24:18.034
And you realize that maybe you haven't really ever made a conscious decision

24:18.530 --> 24:21.394
to invite Jesus to be the Lord and the Savior of your life.

24:22.736 --> 24:29.605
And at the close of 2025, this is such a great opportunity for you to make your peace with God.

24:30.126 --> 24:37.355
Maybe you've tried so many things this year that just left you, just left you unfulfilled.

24:37.375 --> 24:38.537
You're just not satisfied.

24:38.557 --> 24:40.820
You're searching for the meaning of life.

24:42.602 --> 24:45.386
Maybe you just stumbled upon the reason you were born.

24:47.589 --> 24:48.210
You see,

24:48.386 --> 24:55.156
Every person on earth is trying to find true satisfaction, true love, true, true purpose.

24:55.176 --> 24:58.521
But it's not until you find Jesus that you can find any of those things.

24:59.822 --> 25:01.425
You see, you're created for two things.

25:02.286 --> 25:04.810
You're created to be loved and you're created to love.

25:05.851 --> 25:09.196
But before you can truly love someone else, you've got to understand that you are loved.

25:10.217 --> 25:14.564
The Bible says, for God so loved the world that he gave his one and only son.

25:14.644 --> 25:16.146
You're loved today by God.

25:16.962 --> 25:18.484
You've got to accept that gift.

25:18.704 --> 25:25.353
Many of you have received many nice gifts over the last few days, but the greatest gift you can accept is this gift of his love.

25:27.156 --> 25:31.582
So I'm going to ask you right now, just close your eyes wherever you are, as long as you're not driving.

25:31.602 --> 25:34.666
Just close your eyes and want to say this prayer together.

25:35.327 --> 25:37.089
You're saying, John, I need Jesus.

25:37.850 --> 25:38.451
I've drifted.

25:38.491 --> 25:41.075
I've never made that decision.

25:41.115 --> 25:42.957
This is your opportunity to follow him.

25:44.319 --> 25:46.322
Father God, we thank you today.

25:47.106 --> 25:49.489
to sending your son as a little baby in a manger.

25:51.892 --> 25:54.855
We recognize today that we need you.

25:58.219 --> 26:07.170
So I ask you right now that you would help every person who's listening that is straight or needs to come into a relationship with you that would invite you right now.

26:07.911 --> 26:09.974
You just say, Jesus, come into my heart.

26:11.615 --> 26:13.097
Forgive me of my sins.

26:15.100 --> 26:17.042
Cleanse me with your precious blood.

26:18.786 --> 26:20.148
Help me to live for you.

26:22.811 --> 26:23.191
Amen.

26:24.373 --> 26:24.954
Fantastic.

26:24.974 --> 26:35.427
Well, there's no one in the room cheering, but I'm cheering you because if you set that prayer for the first time or if you've reconnected with God, there's angels in heaven that are cheering you on.

26:35.447 --> 26:41.334
And we're cheering you as loud as we can today because it's the greatest decision that you've made.

26:41.354 --> 26:46.400
And you're going to end this year and start a brand new year knowing that Jesus is your good shepherd.

26:46.681 --> 26:47.762
He's in front of you.

26:47.874 --> 26:50.277
He's beside you and He's right behind you.

26:50.658 --> 26:51.940
You have nothing to fear.

26:51.960 --> 26:58.549
I encourage you to take those seven promises and those 10 declarations into 2026 in Jesus' name.

26:59.030 --> 26:59.411
Amen.

27:00.973 --> 27:02.215
Thanks again for tuning in.

27:02.956 --> 27:10.747
If you said yes to Jesus today by saying the Salvation Prayer, we'd love for you to email connections at soulchurch.com.

27:10.767 --> 27:15.474
So we can talk to you a little bit more about this incredible decision you've just made.

27:15.874 --> 27:21.949
And if at any point in the service, you felt moved to give towards any of our local or global initiatives.

27:21.969 --> 27:24.396
Head to SoulChurch.com.

27:24.416 --> 27:31.233
And don't forget to stay connected with us on Facebook, Instagram and YouTube by searching at SoulChurchUK.

27:31.834 --> 27:33.298
Take care and God bless.

